id: zw_appshw_zniffer
label: Zniffer AppsHw
category: Z-Wave|AppsHw
description: > 
  This SLC component provides support for Z-Wave Zniffer (beta) Application.
  The Z-Wave Zniffer Application provides functionality for capturing and analyzing Z-Wave network traffic and sends it
  through a Serial connection. The Z-Wave PTI appliction is supported in the PC Zniffer application out of the box.
package: Z-Wave
quality: production
metadata:
  sbom:
    reference: zw_sbom_license
config_file:
  - path: protocol/z-wave/platform/SiliconLabs/AppsHw/inc/Zniffer/config/zniffer_config.h
    file_id: zniffer_config
    condition: [device_series_2]
source:
  - path: "protocol/z-wave/platform/SiliconLabs/AppsHw/src/Zniffer/Zniffer_hw.c"
include:
  - path: "protocol/z-wave/Apps/zwave_ncp_zniffer"
    file_list:
      - path: "Zniffer_hw.h"
provides:
  - name: zw_appshw_zniffer
requires:
  - name: zw_appshw
